div.div: Special Martial Arts Extreme Hell Private High School

A teenager decides to enroll in a Martial Arts High school so he can learn how to defend himself and not get bullied anymore. But the school he has chosen to enroll in is not like all other typical martial arts schools and he will soon be caught up by a surprise!

Zhu Yunwen, who barely survived the Jingnan campaign received the souls of two of the world's strongest martial artists. The First Heavenly Demon of the Demonic Cult and Huineng, the Sixth Patriarch of the Shaolin Temple in his body and was reborn as a Pacheon.
This is where the story of the Heaven Destroyer's journey toward absolute supremacy begins!
(Source: Naver, Translated)
